    "body": "@Vitruves FYI, I managed to work around this issue following some recommendations in a Reddit thread. Setting `add_newline = false` and adding the following `precmd` before including starship in `.zshrc` worked for me:\r\n\r\n```\r\nprecmd() {\r\n        precmd() {\r\n                echo\r\n        }\r\n}\r\neval \"$(starship init zsh)\"\r\n```",
